des: Pawcutuck North Stonington 9 to 10 Softball division games schedule by the next game number. Game times, ballfield, and opponent teams are provided. No personal information is being used within this skill and is nothing is being collected or saved. This skill is a simple aide to help teams find their ballfield when they arrive at the games. Say your team name to hear the next time, field, and opponent your team is playing. The two team names are Evering Electric and Niners.
